#  - Expanded USPS-style suffix canon + variants
#  - Route/Highway deterministic patterns (RT/RTE/ROUTE, I-93, US-1, MA-9)
#  - No BOM. mkdir output dirs. collisions => UNKNOWN. no fuzzy, no nearest
# ============================================================

